And the moment it was updated to Berl√≠n.
<img width="808" alt="Captura_transicion_berlin" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/81416738/224959942-b33f9716-9841-4881-9db9-3c4fcdd505b8.PNG">


In order to test it in Remix IDE, i compiled the SC for Berlin EVM version and call sendViaTransfer, sendViaCall and sendViaSend functions, and all failed.
<img width="609" alt="TX_failed" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/81416738/224960187-0816889e-788a-4b46-b7e9-3944e768ddd6.PNG">

And when i compiled the same SC for Constantinople EVM version, and call the same send functions, it worked.
<img width="582" alt="TX_success" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/81416738/224960271-d511dec6-2465-4627-bc9b-6beaeb505824.PNG">


